      "acceptanceCriteria": "Solver must have documented V&V test suite with regression testing and configuration management at SQA level 4 for MRL 5 device.",
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (STAR-CCM+) has vendor-supplied verification documentation but no project-specific SQA plan was established. Configuration management records are incomplete. Achieved level 2 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Numerical code verification",
      "type": "CredibilityFactor",
      "requiredLevel": 4,
