      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Iterative convergence residuals and round-off error bounds must be documented for each operating condition simulation.",
      "rationale": "Solver residual convergence criteria applied but not systematically documented across all five operating conditions. Round-off error analysis not performed. Flagged as epistemic gap at MRL 5. Achieved level 1 against required level 4."
    },
    {
      "factorStandard": "ASME-VV40-2018",
      "factorType": "Use error",
